    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>A comparative analysis of selected national jurisdictions with respect to Covid-19 policy response indicated that factors such as effective communications and effective targeted intervention in the environments of higher epidemiological risk can be the key factors in the overall effectiveness of the epidemiological response minimizing both the impact of the epidemics and disruptions in the life of the society.</jats:p>",
